Package: statart
Title: Tidy Functions with Stata Functionality
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Minghong", "Shen", , "mhshenaa@connect.ust.hk", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Enhanced versions of core Stata functions like tab(), fre(), summ(), codebook(), and row_mean(), among others. Designed to work smoothly with tidyverse packages, it also includes functions for data import/export, regression, plotting, and other useful tools.
